==English==
===Noun===
'''cohesion'''
#the state of [[cohering]], or of [[sticking]] [[together]]
#{{physics}},{{chemistry}} the various [[intermolecular]] [[force]]s that hold [[solid]]s and [[liquid]]s together
#{{biology}} the [[growing]] together of normally [[distinct]] parts of a [[plant]]
#{{computing}} the [[degree]] to which different [[module]]s in a [[computing]] [[system]] are [[functionaly]] [[dependent]] on others
